  Kian3-tiok8 le2-pai3-tng5 e5 kang-lang5 ka7 bok8-su kong2: “Bok8-su ah, kam2 e7-sai2 ma5-hoan5 li2 chiong hit-e5 ou-bah-sang2 e5 500 khou the3 heng5 i, i put-si5 to lai5 tui3 goan2 choe3 e5 khang-khoe3 liam7-tang liam7-sai, koh kong2 kian3-tiok8 hong7-hian3 i u7 hian3 500 khou leh ......” 
  Kui toa7-tin7 e5 kui2-a2 chu7-chip8 ti7 chit8-keng le2-pai3-tng5. Chiah-e5 kui2-a2 chin li7-hai7, e7 chhiuN3 Seng3-si, e7 thak8 Seng3-keng, ia7 e7 ki5-to2, koh sian koaN2 to koaN2 boe7 chau2. 
  Ho2-ka-chai3, au7--lai5 u7 chit8-e5 chin u7 leng5-lek8 e5 bok8-su lai5 koaN2 ...... I chiong hong7-hian3-te7-a2 ng3 kui2-a2 tu--chhut-khi3, sou2-u7 e5 kui2-a2 chau2 kah na2 teh poe leh. 
  Chiah8-png7 cheng5, chit8-e5 gin2-a2 chhoa7 ki5-to2: “Kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, siuN2-su3 goan2 hong-hu3 e5 bi2-niu5 chhai3-se. Kho3 Chu2 e5 mia5, a-men ...... tak8-jit8 long2 chiah-e5 chhai3!”
  Li2 tiuN2-lo2 sit8-chai7 si7 u7-kau3 bo5-eng5. Le2-pai3-jit8 oaN7 i su-hoe7 koh ai3 cho3 seng-li2. Bo5-eng5 liau2, chong5 khi3 kau3 kau3-hoe7 i2-keng 10 tiam2 chhiau-koe3 5 hun. I chiu7 toa7-liap8-koaN7 kiaN5 chiuN7 tai5-a2-teng2, khoaN3 chiu-po3, toa7-siaN hoah: “Seng3-si 57 khou ...... ah, sit-le2 sit-le2, seng3-si 57 kin.” 
  Chit8-tin7 kau3-hoe7 hoe7-iu2 le2-pai3 soah, lai5 chhoe7 tiuN2-lo2: “TiuN2-lo2 ah, lan2 e5 bok8-su si7 teh kang2 siaN2 to7 ? Goan2 tak8 le2-pai3 liau2 si5-kan sai2 hiah-ku2 e5 chhia lai5 cho3 le2-pai3, bok8-su kong2 he si7 siaN2 to7-li2 lah ? TiuN2-lo2 ah, li2 kong2 khoaN3-mai7 leh, li2 lai5 cho3 le2-pai3 u7 tit-tioh8 siaN2 ?” 
  TiuN2-lo2 kong2: “Tit-tioh8 an-hioh, tit-tioh8 hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3, hiaN-ti7 chi2-boe7 e5 kau-gi5 ......” 
  Hoe7-iu2 kong2: “Goan2 m7-si7 kong2 che lah, goan2 si7 kong2, li2 thiaN kang2-to7. Oh8-tioh8 siaN2 ?” 
  TiuN2-lo2 kong2: “Oh8 thun-lun2.” 
  (Hong-hiong3 Te7 18 ki5, 1992 ni5 3 goeh8) 
